| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4093 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 633882f5-484f-5ca4-a5a5-d1a9223226f9"
